claim.claim-text:
1. A feed reservoir for use with an animal feeder, the animal feeder including a feed dispensing assembly, the feed reservoir comprising:
a flexible bag for holding a feed material, the flexible bag configured to couple to the feed dispensing assembly to provide a continuous supply of the feed material to the feed dispensing assembly;
wherein air is substantially inhibited from entering the flexible bag when the flexible bag is coupled to the feed dispensing assembly.

13. An animal feeder comprising:
a feed reservoir defining a cavity therein, the feed reservoir having a first end defining an access recess and a second end opposite the first end;
liquid feed material at least partially contained within the cavity to define a feed material fluid level;
a cap removably couplable to the first end of the feed reservoir to selectively seal the access recess; and
a feed dispensing assembly coupled to the second end of the feed reservoir, the feed dispensing assembly including a check valve positioned below the feed material fluid level to allow selective access to the cavity, the check valve inhibiting air from entering the cavity unless placed in an activated position, and wherein the check valve may be placed in an activated position by a bird.
